    <item>
      <title>李宁暴跌后承诺回购高达30亿港元的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/li-ning-pledges-share-buyback-of-up-to-hk-3-billion-after-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李宁公司拟斥资高达30亿港元（约合3.84亿美元）回购股票，此举被视为提振市场情绪，此前这家中国运动服装制造商周一因投资者不同意其利用资金购买房产而股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/li-ning-pledges-share-buyback-of-up-to-hk-3-billion-after-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 01:24:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
