      <title>Rachel Kyte 谈 COP28 审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-12/rachel-kyte-on-cop28-review-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自愿碳市场诚信倡议联合主席 Rachel Kyte 讨论了 COP28 的主要收获，并解释了致力于实现净零排放的国家仍然面临的挑战。她在“黎明亚洲”节目中与海迪·斯特劳德-瓦茨交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-12/rachel-kyte-on-cop28-review-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 01:23:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，IDG 考虑以 9.76 亿美元收购奇瑞汽车母公司股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/idg-weighs-976-million-deal-for-chery-auto-s-parent-stake-sources-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，IDG资本正在考虑以高达70亿元人民币（9.76亿美元）的价格从现有股东手中收购奇瑞控股集团有限公司的股票，这可能会让这家收购公司接触到中国为数不多的非上市主要汽车制造商之一。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/idg-weighs-976-million-deal-for-chery-auto-s-parent-stake-sources-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 01:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价稳定在六月以来的最低水平，供应过剩担忧成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+延长和深化减产的承诺未能阻止油价暴跌后，油价稳定在五个月低点上方，供应过剩担忧成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 00:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行警告中国房地产市场低迷将影响交易；有利于日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bank-of-america-banker-warns-china-property-slump-to-last-years-hit-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行(Bank of America Corp.)一位资深银行家表示，中国房地产市场的低迷将持续数年，由于投资者对世界第二大经济体缺乏信心，该行业的交易荒不太可能很快结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bank-of-america-banker-warns-china-property-slump-to-last-years-hit-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
